changeSet.createProcedure:
create TRIGGER dbo.tI_QATREE_QUESTION ON dbo.QATREE_QUESTION FOR insert AS
DECLARE @defect_cd varchar(16), @question_number varchar(10), @out_question_number varchar(10), @from int, @to int, @length int, @question_id uniqueidentifier, @qatree_id uniqueidentifier, @found int, @debug varchar(10)
select @question_number = rtrim(a.QUESTION_NUMBER), @defect_cd = rtrim(c.DEFECT_CD), @question_id = a.QUESTION_ID, @qatree_id = a.QATREE_ID from inserted a, QATREE b, DEFECT c where a.QATREE_ID = b.QATREE_ID and b.DEFECT_ID = c.DEFECT_ID
select @found = CHARINDEX('.', @question_number)
if @found != 0 begin if @found = 2 select @length = 1 else if @found = 3 select @length = 2 else select @length = 3 end else begin select @length = LEN(@question_number) end
if @length = 1 begin select @out_question_number = @defect_cd + '.00' + @question_number end else if @length = 2 begin select @out_question_number = @defect_cd + '.0' + @question_number end else begin
select @out_question_number = @defect_cd + '.' + @question_number end
update QATREE_QUESTION set QUESTION_REFERENCE = @out_question_number where QUESTION_ID = @question_id and QATREE_ID = @qatree_id
